<h4 id="sample-slurm-script-download-with-comments">Sample SLURM script (<a href="/assets/documents/job.slurm">download with comments</a>)</h4>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;h4&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class="code"&gt;
    #!/bin/bash
    &lt;br&gt;
    &lt;br&gt;#SBATCH --nodes=1
    &lt;br&gt;#SBATCH --partition=128x24
    &lt;br&gt;#SBATCH --job-name=my_job
    &lt;br&gt;#SBATCH --mail-type=ALL
    &lt;br&gt;#SBATCH --mail-user=[your_user_name]@ucsc.edu
    &lt;br&gt;#SBATCH --ntasks=1
    &lt;br&gt;#SBATCH --output=%j.out
    &lt;br&gt;#SBATCH --error=%j.err
    &lt;br&gt;
    &lt;br&gt;module load R/R-3.5.0
    &lt;br&gt;
    &lt;br&gt;R --no-save &lt; script.R
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Sample R script that saves an object as an RDS file that you can download [&lt;a href="documents/script.R"&gt;download with comments&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class="code"&gt;
    r_object &lt;- 1*1
    &lt;br&gt;
    &lt;br&gt;saveRDS(r_object, file = "test.rds")
&lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>
